# This outer Git repository protects local ComfyUI workflow edits.
# It intentionally ignores almost everything in ComfyUI and only tracks the
# small files that are useful to review, diff, and restore.

*

!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!README-GIT-WORKFLOW.md

!.githooks/
!.githooks/**

!tools/
!tools/**

!user/
user/**
!user/default/
user/default/**
!user/default/workflows/
user/default/workflows/**
!user/default/workflows/**/
!user/default/workflows/**/*.json
!user/default/comfy.settings.json

